# Base URL of the SmartFolio backend API.
# Local dev: leave unset — the client defaults to http://localhost:8000.
# Production: set this in your Vercel project's Environment Variables to your
# deployed backend URL, e.g. https://smartfolio-api.onrender.com
#
# NOTE: Vite inlines this at BUILD time, so after changing it in Vercel you must
# trigger a redeploy for it to take effect.
VITE_API_URL=
